Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.86,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What you want？　言いなさいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:54.32,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}All I want！Only you！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:58.12,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,どんなやり込み要素を盛り込んでいても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:01.08,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,思い込みが過ぎてるでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:04.12,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,こうじゃないと言いたいハッピーエンド
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:06.75,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}意味不明の世迷い言を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:10.09,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}空想だった感情が現実に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.59,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Ah！Cool！ You’re cool！Beautiful！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:16.30,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}平穏だった日常が乱雑に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:18.60,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I can’t believe！ You have to leave！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:20.64,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,10)\fad(200,200)}好きも
